				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BB%ABa-%C3%82n/B%E1%BA%A3o-Ninh-S%C3%B9ng-Ph%C3%BAc-t%E1%BB%B1-bi/poem-yadLYWXRS0UtV15FauZxIQ">Bảo Ninh Sùng Phúc tự bi - 保寧崇福寺碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BB%ABa-%C3%82n/author-d8MSBkSrQsUgYbCqr0kX5g">Lý Thừa Ân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-D%E1%BA%A7n/C%E1%BB%95-B%E1%BA%AFc-Kh%E1%BA%A9u-trung-thu/poem-BERJGgjlbcCaxNbLcExmMA">Cổ Bắc Khẩu trung thu - 古北口中秋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-D%E1%BA%A7n/author-F9Asp3KCMCSzhQ5bwTcKBQ">Tào Dần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/H%E1%BA%A1-d%E1%BA%A1-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-Eatnzd_4EFkNv7pZtXFiqA">Hạ dạ tức sự - 夏夜即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%C3%B4/S%C6%A1n-vi%C3%AAn-ti%E1%BB%83u-mai/poem-zajA3A3mMZVqVM4qen39Mw">Sơn viên tiểu mai - 山園小梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-B%C3%B4/author-LbaVSB66mX6k1U09t5TO2A">Lâm Bô</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%C3%B9-H%E1%BB%AFu/S%C6%B0-S%C6%B0-%C4%91%C3%A0n-b%E1%BA%A3n/poem-903hHfj_Qkx-AgifGr38Fw">Sư Sư đàn bản - 師師檀板</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%C3%B9-H%E1%BB%AFu/author-ZjSu27nDCKsyKWbOwBvzWw">Cù Hữu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/Th%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu-qu%C3%A1-ph%E1%BB%8Fng/poem-2iTwMuNBC_qzpT1a-jtS6Q">Thân hữu quá phỏng - 親友過訪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/author-QedIvlr4BuYMTZh_TuTCTA">Nguyễn Đức Đạt</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thang-Hi%E1%BB%83n-T%E1%BB%95/Th%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%8Bch-tu%C3%BD-%C4%91%C3%A1p-Qu%C3%A2n-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/poem-9Lr_Xakcdd5HyCBHU407uw">Thất tịch tuý đáp Quân Đông - 七夕醉答君東</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thang-Hi%E1%BB%83n-T%E1%BB%95/author-9UfZr60VQz5UUa1JmQS-sw">Thang Hiển Tổ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bch/Th%C3%B9-du-ph%C3%A1n/poem-9NNArZ9kFVtGwc3bbCU_EA">Thù du phán - 茱萸沜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bch/author-28bVUu4eMEqyWDansRayiw">Bùi Địch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/Tr%E1%BB%AB-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-0FUoqqh7D8aLj4boJLIO_w">Trừ tịch - 除夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/author-mhAlF-W1JHQDMsH_S0aV3Q">Hà Như</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BA%B1ng/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-thi-%C4%90%C3%A0n-kh%C3%AA/poem-xyW5vvs-O4xemNnU9p-UDA">Vịnh sử thi - Đàn khê - 詠史詩－檀溪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BA%B1ng/author-QGyhycNQKN2UVF9H-N6Zaw">Hồ Tằng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
